Tanzania tour operators keep tourism mogul in the saddle Adv: 
By Adam Ihucha, eTN Tanzania Correspondent | Jul 31, 2015 Mr. Willy Chambulo Adv: 
ARUSHA, Tanzania â€“ The Tanzania Association of Tour Operators (TATO) has unanimously re-elected, the tourism mogul, Mr. Willy Chambulo, as its chairman to lead the powerful association for another two years.
